OL,3,CJury told pensioner was sawn into 27
OL,4,Cpieces as murder trial begins
OL,6,FThe murder trial of a man accused of
OL,7,Fdismembering another man and dumping
OL,8,Fhis body parts across Greater
OL,9,FManchester has got underway at
OL,10,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,12,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, is accused of
OL,13,Fmurdering 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,14,Fafter parts of his body were found in
OL,15,Fsix locations across Salford and north
OL,16,FManchester on 4 April 2024.
OL,18,FA member of the public discovered Mr
OL,19,FEverett's lower torso and thighs
OL,20,Fwrapped in cling film in an abandoned
OL,21,Fbunker in Kersal Dale nature reserve.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
