OL,6,FThe defendant was caught on CCTV
OL,7,Fmaking numerous trips dumping Mr
OL,8,FEverett's body parts, it is alleged.
OL,10,FMajerkiewicz denies murder and
OL,11,Fmanslaughter.
OL,13,FJason Pitter KC, began opening the
OL,14,Fcase for the prosecution to the jury
OL,15,Fof six women and six men, with the
OL,16,Ffirst discovery of body parts in the
OL,17,Fnature reserve.
OL,19,F"For obvious reasons it was not known
OL,20,Fwho it was," he said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@LO]
