OL,6,F"Who it is that was responsible for
OL,7,Fmurdering him, cutting him into pieces
OL,8,Fand depositing his body in various
OL,9,Flocations?
OL,11,F"The investigations, the prosecution
OL,12,Fsay, was able to identify those two
OL,13,Fthings: That the body was that of a
OL,14,FStuart Everett, indeed a man of 67
OL,15,Fyears of age at the time he died. The
OL,16,Fperson responsible for killing him was
OL,17,Fthe defendant, Marcin Majerkiewicz."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@dO]
