OL,6,FThe court heard both men lived in a
OL,7,Fhouse in the Winton area of Salford
OL,8,Fand there is "good evidence" to
OL,9,Fsuggest Mr Everett was killed on the
OL,10,Fevening and into the morning of the
OL,11,F27th to the 28th of March of last year.
OL,13,FMr Everett was of Polish heritage and
OL,14,Fwas born with the name Roman Ziemacki.
OL,16,FHe lived at a shared house at 95
OL,17,FWorsely Road, in Winton, as the sole
OL,18,Ftenant, responsible for the rent but
OL,19,Fsub-let rooms in the property, which
OL,20,Fhe sub-let to others including
OL,21,FMajerkiewicz.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@\O]
