OL,6,FAn increase in rent may have led to
OL,7,F"tension" between the two men, the
OL,8,Fcourt heard.
OL,10,FThe prosecutor said after the initial
OL,11,Ftorso find police scoured CCTV from
OL,12,Fthe area around Kersal Dale on April 4
OL,13,F2024.
OL,15,FDetectives found, two days before,
OL,16,Faround 5pm, a man was seen entering
OL,17,Fthe pathway nearby carrying a heavy
OL,18,Fblue bag, walking to the wooded area
OL,19,Fwhere the body part was found.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@IO]
