OL,6,FThe same person was seen to emerge a
OL,7,Fshort while later holding the bag
OL,8,Ffolded up.
OL,10,FMajerkiewicz was traced and arrested
OL,11,Fon suspicion of murder as he matched
OL,12,Fthe man in the CCTV footage, the court
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FHe had two mobile phones, one
OL,16,Fbelonging to Mr Everett along with the
OL,17,Fdead man's bank cards, the court was
OL,18,Ftold.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
