OL,6,FWhen police searched Majerkiewicz's
OL,7,Faddress they found evidence of
OL,8,Fbloodstaining and a clean-up
OL,9,Foperation, showing "something terrible
OL,10,Fhad happened in that house", Mr Pitter
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FAnalysis of Majerkiewicz's phone
OL,14,Fmovements and CCTV footage showed him
OL,15,Fmaking a number of journeys with bags
OL,16,Fbefore returning, the court heard.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@[O]
