OL,6,FAt one location, Chesterfield Close in
OL,7,FWinton, nine packages of body parts
OL,8,Fwere recovered, including many
OL,9,Finternal organs and Mr Everett's
OL,10,Fgenitalia, the court was told.
OL,12,FRecoveries at Linneyshaw Colliery Wood
OL,13,Fincluded body parts wrapped in cling
OL,14,Ffilm, containing bones and muscle
OL,15,Ftissue.
OL,17,FAt Blackleach Reservoir a further six
OL,18,Fbody parts were found, including parts
OL,19,Fof the skull, scalp and left ear and
OL,20,Fparts of the skin from Mr Everett's
OL,21,Fface.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
