OL,6,FAnalysis showed dismemberment of the
OL,7,Fbody was consistent with the use of a
OL,8,Fhacksaw and took place after death,
OL,9,Fbut Mr Pitter added: "It is possible
OL,10,Fthough, that some of the cuts occurred
OL,11,Fwhilst Stuart Everett was alive."
OL,13,FThe trial continues.
